..TEXT:
|Dione~: Daughter of Oceanus and Tethys, Dione was
the mother of Venus, whence Venus is sometimes called Dionaea.
|Cupido~: Pronounced ^Cup@ido.~  Cupid was the well-known son of
Venus.
