..TEXT:
|Ma voi torcete~... |spada~: But you mortals
twist to religion, i.e., force to become a monk or a priest, one
who is born to gird on the sword, to be a warrior.  |fia~ = ^sar@a~
(connoting possibility, as in modern Italian).
